TITLE: Row Level Security Policies
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of RLS policies for projects and project members tables to enforce access control at the database level.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sahilpanhotra/makerkitdocs.git/blob/main/mdDocs/kits/projects_data_model_53.md#2025-04-22_snippet_30

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
create policy select_projects
  on public.projects
  for select
  to authenticated
  using (
    public.is_project_member(id)
  );

create policy insert_new_project
  on public.projects
  for insert
  to authenticated
  with check (
    public.has_role_on_account(account_id)
  );

create policy delete_project
  on public.projects
  for delete
  to authenticated
  using (
    public.can_delete_project((select auth.uid()), id)
  );
```

