TITLE: Comprehensive Multi-Step Form with Account, Profile, and Review Steps
DESCRIPTION: A complete implementation of a multi-step form with three steps: Account, Profile, and Review. It showcases form validation, step navigation, and integrates with Shadcn UI components. Includes a Stepper for progress tracking.
