DESCRIPTION: Implements a React component to display tasks fetched from Firestore using the useFetchTasks hook. The component handles different states such as loading and error and uses other UI components like PageLoadingIndicator and Alert for better user experience.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sahilpanhotra/makerkitdocs.git/blob/main/mdDocs/kits/deploying_production_development_getting_started_environment_variables_13.md#2025-04-22_snippet_13

