TITLE: Creating RLS Policy for Tasks
DESCRIPTION: SQL policy definition to ensure tasks can only be accessed by users within the same organization through membership verification.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sahilpanhotra/makerkitdocs.git/blob/main/mdDocs/kits/organization_sdk_organization_subscription_sdk_sdk_25.md#2025-04-22_snippet_27

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
create policy "Tasks can be read by users of the organizations to which it belongs" on tasks
  for all
    using (
      exists (
        select
          1
        from
          memberships
        where
          user_id = auth.uid () and
          tasks.organization_id = memberships.organization_id
      )
    );
```

