TITLE: Encrypting API Keys in Firestore with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript snippet demonstrates how to encrypt and store API keys in Firestore, and decrypt them when retrieved. Requires 'SECRET_KEY' in environment variables for encrypting and decrypting data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/sahilpanhotra/makerkitdocs.git/blob/main/mdDocs/kits/commands_cors_develop_firebase_security_rules_5.md#2025-04-22_snippet_26

