DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript function demonstrates how to consume credits within a Remix application's route handler. It simulates an API call (`callOpenAIApi`), retrieves the usage cost, initializes an admin Supabase client (`getSupabaseRouteHandlerClient`), and calls the `consume_credits` RPC function to deduct the tokens from the user's account.
