TITLE: Using Custom Mutation Hook in a React Component
DESCRIPTION: This TSX snippet demonstrates the usage of the `useCreateSession` custom hook within a React functional component. It destructures `trigger`, `error`, `isMutating`, and `data` from the hook's return value to manage the API request lifecycle, display loading/error/success feedback, and trigger the sign-in API call via a `SignInForm` component's `onSignIn` prop.
