DESCRIPTION: A comprehensive React component implementing a multi-step onboarding form with three stages: profile creation, team setup, and plan selection. Uses React Hook Form for form management, Zod for validation, and includes dynamic checkout integration. The component features a stepper UI, form validation, and responsive design with animated transitions.
