TITLE: Creating Tasks Table Schema with RLS
DESCRIPTION: SQL schema definition for tasks table with organization relationship and Row Level Security (RLS) policy implementation
SOURCE: https://github.com/sahilpanhotra/makerkitdocs.git/blob/main/mdDocs/kits/user_sdk_sdk_ci_tests_84.md#2025-04-22_snippet_22

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
create table tasks (
  id bigint generated always as identity primary key,
  organization_id bigint not null references public.organizations,
  name text not null,
  description text,
  done bool not null,
  due_date timestamptz not null
);
```

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
alter table tasks enable row level security;

create policy "Tasks can be read by users of the organizations to which it belongs" on tasks
  for all
    using (
      exists (
        select
          1
        from
          memberships
        where
          user_id = auth.uid () and
          tasks.organization_id = memberships.organization_id
      )
    );
```

